latestIgtvVideos.title: The box - an original
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Cardboard walls is all I’m used to,
These eyes they all stare down at the truth.
But as I grow,
This box can’t hold me anymore.
So they place the bricks,
Weigh it down,
Send me afloat.

But when I break through ,
And see the blue
Sea around me, it looks so pretty.
And I’m not upset or confused,
Cause maybe all I needed was a change of view.
And I got it.
.
.
.

#Gini #RollingStoneIndia #CoverStar #FutureOfMusic2025

Gini (@this.is.gini) is quietly changing the face of Indian pop. The 19-year-old stars on the cover of Rolling Stone India’s April 2025 “Future of Music” issue. In the feature, the “Sukoon” singer opens up about her roots, spending countless hours on Clubhouse during the pandemic, growing a loyal community, and eventually taking the plunge to chase music full-time. With nearly half a million Spotify listeners and a sold-out tour to her name, Gini’s just getting warmed up.

Read the story and see photos at the link in our bio.

Our “Future of Music” special print edition drops soon.
